{"tid":1615370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家重要咁傻豬？","createTime":"2019-10-03T05:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:01:59.000Z","uid":254505,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1e9beda35523a3af1ae13f3a9b6f4a4778d346","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"十月一號用實彈促意謀殺 <br />\n另外全日一過開左六槍<br />\n<br />\n十月二號西九龍裁判法院外有狗持實彈步槍戒備 <br />\n晚上各區活動 班失去理性嘅狗不斷打街坊鬧街坊 <br />\n但我見好多傻豬重用遮同水馬中間條膠塞做武器<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解大家重要咁傻豬？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根本比佢捉到既話 你用遮佢都屈你改裝過 <br />\n分分鐘用假證物提堂 目的係將你告至「藏有攻擊性武器」既最高刑罰<br />\n<br />\n橫掂都係死 點解大家唔用鐵通錘仔呀？<br />\n(刀唔建議 容易傷到自己人 專家另計)<br />\n<br />\n使用武力既心態有提升確實值得一讚<br />\n但除左心態提升之外 武器都要提升<br />\n用遮扑佢一百下都及唔上鐵通/錘仔一下<br />\n一方面提高對狗隻既損傷 <br />\n另一方面減低自己人被咬風險<br />\n<br />\n有幾多次係成班人打一隻狗<br />\n最後狗隻增援走得慢既手足被咬<br />\n而被打既狗施施然起身拍一拍件衫d塵一d事都冇<br />\n你諗下如果三兩秒搞掂一隻 成個攻勢係幾咁順暢<br />\n<br />\n大家無謂再比道德枷鎖綁住自己<br />\n班狗點解會贏我地係因為佢地冇道德枷鎖<br />\n明明大家講好咗核爆都唔割 <br />\n大家仲有咩好顧慮？<br />\n<br />\n我記得好多人話如果開實彈就點點點<br />\n一早荃灣向天鳴槍開左槍啦但打唔中人大家就算數<br />\n<br />\n到十月一打中人喇 <br />\n手足大命死唔去大家又好似諗住算數<br />\n<br />\n係咪就算對家用機槍掃射<br />\n大家都淨係匿喺Facebook屌鬼就算？<br />\n<br />\n求下大家 心態同裝備都要升級<br />\n個個開口埋口話革命 要打仗要革命講咩道理<br />\n打贏嗰個就係道理 孫中山起義唔通冇殺死過人咩<br />\n歷史會記住我們 歷史會證明一切<br />\n如果我地輸左 死去既朋友就死得毫無意義<br />\n<br />\n祝各位武運鏗鏘<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"721d28fe2ec284aa9456645ac1c3800648330288","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"ff4ec38dd61450179e5a1b7498f986b096c819d2","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9d025ab0db63a0b17d1968f489f82e38061e18c9","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b6533c8eb1db58c6ba351459cd65cd68dfa1358d","tid":1615370,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc31c2b35378539b750352fcf7e3615aa0c113d","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"379e3be658d0fc3da7088acd8d6a5a2df3daba50","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"48c2f3e08bc9880897c27d48e8f58e7e502a90fe","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"271a77286062ac5673b878959efdb605043a8fb2","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8ff8aeb1d47d1df49b4d961a9eb39b3a5e4d266f","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"61de989ac086308b65522132f70e785f31295b44","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"11131ec1b602f1b5179d111714e5ab145e5ae6fa","tid":1615370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"1"}]}